    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIRCAL\nSYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEffective June 1, 1985\nVANCOUVER\nBriti 1i Columbia",
      "FLY AIRCAL AND EARN FREE TRIPS TO THE WORLD!\ncondon\ntong tong\nNORTHWEST ORIENT\nStarting July 1st AirCal frequent travelers can\nearn free trips to exciting places like New York,\nHonolulu, Hong Kong or London. Our new frequent\ntraveler connection with Northwest Orient Airlines\nmakes seeing the world easy! But that's just the\nbeginning...\nAfter July 1st AirCal AirFair members who\nfly Northwest Orient can have those flight miles\ncredited to their AirFair accounts. Imagine how\nquickly those miles can add up! We're proud to\njoin forces with Northwest Orient to help bring\nthe world a little closer, a little easier.\nFor more details, ask an AirCal representative.\nAnd if you are not yet a member of the AirFair\nprogram, ask for an enrollment form and join today.\nAIRCAL\nAIRFAIR\nFrequent Traveler Program\nP.O. Box Z, Newport Beach, CA 92658-2619"
    ],
